Body: Description: Hello Team, Please help me to clean up the space on my server. https://b8sond5.hosted.endpointprotector.com/
What We've Learned Updated: Client is requesting to clear up some space on their AWS side.
Next Steps Updated: Asked for approval first to access their SSH and will get back.
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
Invitation updated. Attendees: Marian Ilies, Adrian Draghici, Saikat Banerjee
Invitation updated. Attendees: Marian Ilies, Adrian Draghici

What We've Learned Updated: We've connected remote with Saikat and explained his two options.
Either he needs to set up the system back up with logs older than 1 month to run as currently he had older than 4 months(which had nothing) or he could try to increase the disk space size(for that he needs to contact his account manager to discuss because he's hosting the appliance on our AWS).

Currently we adjusted the system back up V2 to take logs older than 1 month as well as the scheduled back up.

Agreed to keep the ticket opened and let us know tomorrow if the space is cleared.
Next Steps Updated: Will send a follow up note.
